WEBVTT

00:13:59.515 --> 00:14:04.464
My room, my books, myself,

00:14:04.464 --> 00:14:10.122
and everything that was making me smile.

00:14:10.122 --> 00:14:14.250
Oh, oh, I had so many dreams

00:14:14.250 --> 00:14:17.796
that were about to be realized."

00:14:19.323 --> 00:14:21.551
So here is my point:

00:14:21.551 --> 00:14:23.597
Not investing in refugees

00:14:23.597 --> 00:14:29.241
is a huge missed opportunity.

00:14:29.241 --> 00:14:31.092
Leave them abandoned,